'''''môr''''' is a noun meaning "darkness, dark, night" in [[Sindarin]]. Compare with ''[[morë]]'' in [[Quenya]].

Examples:
* [[Mordor]] = "Black Land"
* [[Morwen]] = "Dark Maiden"

==See also==

*[[Sindarin]] ''[[morn]]'' ("black, dark")
